WEBVTT

01:34.320 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:38.400 --> 01:40.320
Java is a powerful language.

01:40.400 --> 01:42.480
It can be used to develop
different types of software systems

01:42.560 --> 01:43.880
at various levels

01:43.960 --> 01:45.960
and for different application contexts.

01:46.640 --> 01:48.360
In recent years, cloud computing

01:48.440 --> 01:50.360
and big data have become very popular.

01:50.440 --> 01:53.120
Java is applied in software systems

01:53.200 --> 01:55.080
with different application contexts
in these fields.

01:55.960 --> 01:58.200
It is known for its high fault tolerance.

01:58.800 --> 02:00.960
It can be deployed on low-cost,

02:01.040 --> 02:02.000
general software.

02:02.080 --> 02:03.200
It is suitable for software

02:03.280 --> 02:04.840
that involves
storing massive amounts of data.

02:04.920 --> 02:05.760
SECOND-CLASS SEAT AVAILABLE

02:22.920 --> 02:26.040
YIHE

02:51.120 --> 02:57.160
YIHE UNIVERSITY

03:51.200 --> 03:52.600
3,399 DAYS

03:53.440 --> 03:57.320
BEIYU TUNNEL 3 RESCUE, HOUR 13

03:57.400 --> 03:58.800
BEIYU

04:04.600 --> 04:06.040
NEWS REPORTING VEHICLE

04:06.120 --> 04:07.480
Everyone, hurry up. Move quickly.

04:07.560 --> 04:08.920
Grab your stuff and follow me, quickly!

04:09.000 --> 04:10.960
- What are you guys doing?
- Hello.

04:11.040 --> 04:12.440
We're reporters from Nanwu TV station.

04:13.160 --> 04:14.200
Hurry up!

04:14.280 --> 04:16.360
- Catch up, quick!
- Don't cross the blockade line.

04:16.440 --> 04:17.279
It's very dangerous there now.

04:17.360 --> 04:18.279
Got it. Thank you.

04:18.360 --> 04:19.720
- No need.
- Hurry up!

04:29.320 --> 04:31.800
Everyone, remember this.
Find your positions.

04:32.320 --> 04:34.840
Remember this.
Don't interfere with the rescue.

04:34.920 --> 04:35.960
Stay safe.

04:36.040 --> 04:37.400
Oh my God.

04:37.480 --> 04:40.080
I will never watch disaster movies again.
This is really scary.

04:41.240 --> 04:43.480
This is what
being a reporter is all about.

04:43.560 --> 04:44.920
We're here to show the truth

04:45.000 --> 04:46.320
to our viewers.

04:55.280 --> 04:57.400
A serious mudslide occurred
at Beiyu Tunnel 3.

04:57.480 --> 04:58.360
Currently, it is known

04:58.440 --> 05:00.080
seven vehicles are trapped
inside the tunnel.

05:00.160 --> 05:01.400
After the incident,

05:01.480 --> 05:03.560
the municipal government immediately
activated the rescue plan.

05:03.640 --> 05:04.920
I will now provide a deeper report.

05:05.000 --> 05:06.360
- Miss, please stop!
- Yu!

05:06.440 --> 05:07.280
It's dangerous ahead. You can't go in!

05:07.360 --> 05:08.560
- She's a family member.
- Save my daughter!

05:08.640 --> 05:09.760
Her name is Shi Jiayu!

05:09.840 --> 05:11.920
Family members, please rest to the side.
Please stay calm.

05:12.000 --> 05:13.120
- Save my daughter!
- If you go in now,

05:13.200 --> 05:14.280
it will interfere with our rescue.

05:14.360 --> 05:16.160
Please rest to the side. Is that okay?

05:16.240 --> 05:18.040
- Family members, please rest to the side.
- Let's rest over there.

05:18.120 --> 05:19.160
Is that okay?

05:27.960 --> 05:30.280
Yifan, let's continue…

05:31.320 --> 05:32.440
Yifan?

05:33.640 --> 05:35.680
- What's wrong?
- I'm fine.

05:35.760 --> 05:36.760
So far,

05:36.840 --> 05:39.840
more than a dozen injured
have been successfully rescued.

05:39.920 --> 05:41.000
They are being sent
to the hospital for treatment.

05:41.080 --> 05:42.960
It is understood
that the cause of the accident

05:43.040 --> 05:44.560
was the continuous heavy rain.

05:44.640 --> 05:46.640
This is a disaster
that caught everyone by surprise.

05:46.720 --> 05:50.120
Stay tuned
for further reports by Nanwu TV.

05:52.600 --> 05:54.120
You've worked hard.

05:54.200 --> 05:55.200
It's nothing.

05:55.280 --> 05:56.880
I hope they're rescued soon.

05:58.280 --> 05:59.200
You're taking a break?

05:59.280 --> 06:00.680
- Ms. Qian.
- No need to get up.

06:00.760 --> 06:01.640
Just take a break.

06:02.160 --> 06:04.720
Well, Fu Zhuang, Yifan,

06:04.800 --> 06:06.520
I'll need you both

06:07.120 --> 06:08.320
to stay here a bit longer.

06:08.400 --> 06:10.680
If anything happens,
keep in touch with me at any time.

06:10.760 --> 06:11.600
Don't worry.

06:11.680 --> 06:14.120
If anything happens,
we'll communicate in the group.

06:15.480 --> 06:17.080
How come you're bleeding here?

06:18.400 --> 06:19.560
Are you okay?

06:23.240 --> 06:24.200
It's nothing serious.

06:24.280 --> 06:25.920
It's probably a scratch from the debris.

06:26.000 --> 06:27.600
Do you need to get it treated?

06:27.680 --> 06:29.680
Maybe find some medicine and disinfect it.

06:29.760 --> 06:30.880
It's really nothing serious.

06:30.960 --> 06:32.120
You can go back to the rest area now.

06:32.200 --> 06:33.720
- Are you really okay?
- I'm really fine.

06:33.800 --> 06:34.840
Be careful.

06:34.920 --> 06:36.000
Then we'll head back first.

06:36.080 --> 06:37.320
Be sure to stay safe, you two.

06:37.400 --> 06:38.240
Communicate with us anytime
if something happens.

06:38.320 --> 06:39.160
Okay.

06:39.240 --> 06:40.320
- We're leaving first.
- Thank you, Yifan.

06:40.400 --> 06:41.560
- You've worked hard today.
- You, too.

06:47.360 --> 06:48.920
You've worked hard. Rest early tonight.

06:49.000 --> 06:50.280
You too, get some rest.

07:08.240 --> 07:09.120
What's wrong?

07:10.000 --> 07:11.680
I've never seen so much blood.

07:13.160 --> 07:15.160
You'll get used to it.
It's inevitable in journalism.

07:24.000 --> 07:25.280
Drink some water.

07:25.800 --> 07:26.680
Thank you.

07:26.760 --> 07:28.160
Wash up and go to bed early.

07:28.240 --> 07:30.120
If you feel unwell, wake me up.

07:30.200 --> 07:31.200
Don't feel embarrassed.

07:31.280 --> 07:32.560
Thank you, Yifan.

07:53.880 --> 07:56.200
SANG YAN

07:56.280 --> 07:57.680
SANG YAN: HOW'S IT GOING?

08:02.520 --> 08:06.760
I'M FINE, AND EVERYTHING'S OKAY

08:19.240 --> 08:22.360
BEIYU TUNNEL 3 RESCUE, HOUR 38

08:31.640 --> 08:33.080
Yifan, Fang Li.

08:33.159 --> 08:34.880
Ms. Qian is calling us to head out.

08:34.960 --> 08:36.240
Quick.

08:36.320 --> 08:37.360
Let's go.

08:42.640 --> 08:47.640
BEIYU TUNNEL 3 RESCUE, HOUR 46

08:53.840 --> 08:55.880
We've found a suspected survivor here!

08:56.680 --> 08:57.680
It looks like another person was rescued!

09:10.760 --> 09:12.080
Come on. Dig faster!

09:13.120 --> 09:14.000
Everyone, dig with your hands!

09:14.840 --> 09:16.480
Come on, little one.

09:17.000 --> 09:18.200
I found a little girl inside.

09:18.280 --> 09:19.120
More people, come over here!

09:19.200 --> 09:20.160
Come on, girl.

09:20.240 --> 09:21.480
There's a child. Be careful!

09:21.560 --> 09:22.400
- Do it gently.
- Come on.

09:22.480 --> 09:23.280
Come on, little one.

09:23.360 --> 09:24.400
- Give me your hand.
- Mind her head.

09:24.480 --> 09:25.320
My dad's still inside.

09:25.400 --> 09:26.600
Yu!

09:27.200 --> 09:28.040
- Mind her head.
- Be careful.

09:28.120 --> 09:29.320
Save my dad…

09:29.400 --> 09:31.480
- Little one.
- Little one, lie down.

09:32.640 --> 09:34.640
My dad's still inside…

09:34.720 --> 09:35.560
Get the ambulance closer!

09:35.640 --> 09:37.840
Your dad will be out soon.

09:37.920 --> 09:39.080
The skylight's too small.

09:39.160 --> 09:41.520
My dad can't crawl out…

09:44.080 --> 09:45.840
Save my dad…

09:46.560 --> 09:47.600
Be careful.

09:47.680 --> 09:48.880
Do it gently.

09:48.960 --> 09:50.080
Hurry, get her in the ambulance!

09:50.160 --> 09:51.280
Dad…

09:52.120 --> 09:53.880
- Yu!
- Dad…

09:53.960 --> 09:55.680
- My dad's still inside…
- Yu!

09:55.760 --> 09:57.560
Ambulance, open the door! Hurry!

09:57.640 --> 09:58.840
- Be careful.
- Yu, don't be scared.

09:58.920 --> 10:00.160
Mom's here. Don't be scared!

10:00.240 --> 10:01.200
Dad…

10:01.280 --> 10:02.560
Yu! Yu, don't be scared.

10:02.640 --> 10:04.760
- Mom's here!
- Dad's still inside…

10:07.680 --> 10:09.000
Dad…

10:12.840 --> 10:14.800
Yu, don't be scared.
Mom's here. Don't cry.

10:17.680 --> 10:20.360
Hello, everyone.
I'm Su Tian, a reporter from Nanwu TV.

10:20.440 --> 10:23.080
We've just learned
that among the 17 rescued victims,

10:23.160 --> 10:24.680
14 have minor injuries,

10:24.760 --> 10:26.160
and three have more severe injuries.

10:26.240 --> 10:27.760
They are currently receiving treatment.

10:27.840 --> 10:30.560
The one most people are concerned about
is seven-year-old girl Shi Jiayu.

10:30.640 --> 10:32.880
She is still under observation in the ICU.

10:32.960 --> 10:35.520
Any latest updates will be brought
to you as soon as possible.

10:35.600 --> 10:36.880
Is Shi Jiayu still in the ICU?

10:36.960 --> 10:38.200
Please wait. I'll check

10:38.280 --> 10:40.880
if she's been moved from the ICU
to a regular ward.

10:40.960 --> 10:42.640
- Should we do an interview?
- Yes.

10:44.280 --> 10:46.080
I originally planned to take Yu abroad

10:46.160 --> 10:48.160
for immigration next month.

10:48.240 --> 10:49.880
I've divorced her father.

10:50.800 --> 10:53.760
This time, it's a farewell trip
between her and her father.

10:56.880 --> 10:57.920
But…

10:58.600 --> 11:00.000
I never imagined

11:00.080 --> 11:02.840
we'd encounter such a disaster.

11:03.480 --> 11:06.280
Now, Yu's father's life and death
are still unknown.

11:06.920 --> 11:08.320
I really have no idea

11:08.400 --> 11:09.800
how to tell Yu about this

11:09.880 --> 11:11.840
when she wakes up…

11:11.920 --> 11:13.400
It's okay. Everything will be fine.

11:14.720 --> 11:16.040
Your daughter's medication
has been changed.

11:16.120 --> 11:18.280
- You can go visit her now.
- Okay.

11:30.600 --> 11:32.000
Mom.

11:32.080 --> 11:34.120
Tian, how's everything over there?

11:34.720 --> 11:36.120
I didn't want to disturb you yesterday.

11:36.200 --> 11:37.920
Is it dangerous over there?

11:38.000 --> 11:39.600
It's not dangerous. Everything's fine.

11:40.760 --> 11:42.120
How's the baby? Let me see.

11:42.200 --> 11:44.320
Okay. Look.

11:44.400 --> 11:45.680
Look, the baby's asleep.

11:46.400 --> 11:47.480
She's asleep?

11:49.640 --> 11:51.160
Mom, you've worked hard.

11:52.000 --> 11:54.160
I still have some things to do.
I'll hang up now.

11:54.240 --> 11:56.160
Okay, go ahead.

11:56.240 --> 11:57.680
Be sure to stay safe.

12:03.960 --> 12:05.240
What's wrong?

12:05.840 --> 12:06.760
Is everything fine at home?

12:06.840 --> 12:07.920
Yes.

12:08.000 --> 12:09.840
- Is the baby fine?
- She's fine.

12:11.800 --> 12:14.360
Alright, tomorrow,
you don't need to go to the site.

12:15.040 --> 12:16.600
Just stay at the hospital and keep watch.

12:17.320 --> 12:19.760
It's alright, Ms. Qian.
I'm recovering well after childbirth.

12:20.520 --> 12:22.560
The hospital also needs someone to stay.

12:22.640 --> 12:23.880
Don't overthink it.

12:26.200 --> 12:28.360
- Thank you, Ms. Qian.
- No need to be polite.

12:29.080 --> 12:30.800
Alright, stop crying.

12:35.520 --> 12:38.160
This vehicle
was overturned due to the impact

12:38.240 --> 12:39.760
of the mudslide.

12:39.840 --> 12:43.080
Fortunately, a tree broken by the stones

12:43.160 --> 12:44.560
was positioned over the vehicle.

12:44.640 --> 12:48.080
This created a narrow survival space.

12:48.160 --> 12:51.240
So, the little girl
could escape through the skylight.

12:52.320 --> 12:54.480
But the skylight was very small.

12:54.560 --> 12:56.080
The little girl's father, Mr. Shi,

12:56.160 --> 12:57.720
is still trapped in the car.

12:57.800 --> 13:00.600
Excuse me, Leader Li. Is it possible
to determine her father's location

13:00.680 --> 13:01.960
from the place
where the little girl was rescued?

13:02.040 --> 13:04.040
There was hope at first.

13:04.120 --> 13:06.600
However,
there was another collapse just now.

13:06.680 --> 13:09.280
The vehicle shifted
and got buried even deeper.

13:10.200 --> 13:13.200
Although the difficulty
of the rescue is great,

13:13.280 --> 13:15.160
as long as there's a sliver of hope,

13:15.240 --> 13:17.360
- we will never give up!
- Thank you.

13:17.440 --> 13:19.920
And you media colleagues,
please be sure to stay safe.

13:20.000 --> 13:20.880
Excuse me. Let me pass.

13:21.480 --> 13:22.920
Leader Li, we've dug out Mr. Shi!

13:23.000 --> 13:24.680
- We got him?
- We've dug out Mr. Shi!

13:24.760 --> 13:26.320
- Hurry up!
- Hurry!

13:26.400 --> 13:27.560
Watch your step! Quick!

13:27.640 --> 13:29.160
Take care! Stay safe!

13:37.720 --> 13:38.960
My daughter…

13:39.680 --> 13:40.720
is named Yu…

13:57.920 --> 13:59.240
Yifan,

13:59.320 --> 14:01.080
I bought some authentic local breakfast.

14:01.160 --> 14:03.360
It's really delicious. Try it.

14:03.440 --> 14:04.600
Thank you.

14:16.320 --> 14:18.520
- What's wrong?
- Nothing.

14:21.000 --> 14:22.400
Yifan,

14:22.480 --> 14:24.080
I'm starting to admire you more.

14:24.160 --> 14:25.280
You've barely rested,
yet you're not tired.

14:25.360 --> 14:28.960
- I think…
- What?

14:29.680 --> 14:30.720
Nothing.

14:44.800 --> 14:47.160
You can have the breakfast first.
I'm going to reply to a message.

14:59.480 --> 15:01.440
There are nine days left.

15:04.400 --> 15:05.600
Let me know when you receive my message.

15:09.200 --> 15:11.280
When you come back, bring me an apple.

15:18.760 --> 15:20.240
Today's Christmas Eve.

15:23.080 --> 15:24.800
I don't know if I'll get the chance

15:24.880 --> 15:26.640
to make it back before his birthday.

15:31.600 --> 15:34.040
Everyone, gather up! We're heading out!

15:47.880 --> 15:48.880
Hello.

15:49.560 --> 15:52.240
I just arrived at the hotel.
I've been busy all day.

15:52.840 --> 15:54.920
I guessed it. It's alright.

15:57.440 --> 15:59.080
Is everything okay?

15:59.160 --> 16:00.680
Why are you stealing my words?

16:02.240 --> 16:04.400
Your voice sounds tired.

16:04.480 --> 16:06.120
Yeah, a bit.

16:07.040 --> 16:09.320
My eyes are almost too tired to keep open.

16:09.400 --> 16:10.720
I'll sleep in a bit.

16:10.800 --> 16:12.960
Yifan, I'll head back to rest now.

16:13.720 --> 16:15.120
Goodnight, Yifan.

16:18.240 --> 16:19.080
Well…

16:22.520 --> 16:23.840
Goodnight.

16:24.560 --> 16:25.600
Goodnight.

16:26.800 --> 16:28.600
It sounds like
it's raining heavily over there.

16:30.480 --> 16:31.600
Be sure to stay warm.

16:33.440 --> 16:34.640
Okay.

16:53.480 --> 16:55.200
Merry Christmas Eve.

16:57.760 --> 16:59.280
Merry Christmas Eve.

17:38.240 --> 17:39.560
SANG YAN

17:41.960 --> 17:44.080
The apple is just a sketch for now.

17:44.160 --> 17:46.680
I'll get you the real one when I return.

17:58.400 --> 17:59.680
Alright.

17:59.760 --> 18:01.960
Go to sleep. Remember to lock the door.

18:02.040 --> 18:04.040
Don't sleepwalk around.

18:04.120 --> 18:05.680
If you really want to sleepwalk,

18:05.760 --> 18:07.680
just wander around in your room.

18:07.760 --> 18:10.880
Your victim can only be me. Got it?

18:22.760 --> 18:25.000
After continuous efforts
from the rescuers,

18:25.080 --> 18:26.640
the danger at the scene has been cleared.

18:26.720 --> 18:29.200
Tunnel 3 is almost open.

18:29.280 --> 18:33.200
Currently, the 18 rescued victims
are in stable condition.

18:33.280 --> 18:35.600
They are receiving further treatment
and observation at the hospital.

18:36.400 --> 18:38.920
Looking back
at these heart-pounding moments,

18:39.000 --> 18:40.880
we, the First News team from Nanwu TV,

18:40.960 --> 18:43.200
captured every one with our cameras.

18:43.280 --> 18:45.360
Please continue to follow
our ongoing reports.

18:47.840 --> 18:49.880
Alright. Everyone, stay alert.

18:49.960 --> 18:51.280
Let me say a few words.

18:51.800 --> 18:53.880
Fu Zhuang, listen up.
Everyone's worked really hard

18:53.960 --> 18:55.160
over the past few days.

18:55.760 --> 18:57.800
And last night, we stayed up all night.

18:57.880 --> 18:59.480
Sorry for troubling everyone.

18:59.560 --> 19:00.520
But

19:00.600 --> 19:02.800
all the hard work this time
has been worth it.

19:02.880 --> 19:05.960
Our live broadcast and reports
have received attention.

19:06.480 --> 19:07.960
So, when we get back to Nanwu,

19:08.040 --> 19:10.680
I'll treat everyone to a nice meal.
How does that sound?

19:10.760 --> 19:11.600
Great!

19:11.680 --> 19:13.040
Thanks, Ms. Qian!

19:14.040 --> 19:15.280
By the way, there's one more thing.

19:15.360 --> 19:18.320
The report on the trapped victims,
Shi Lei and his family,

19:18.400 --> 19:20.280
is really gaining traction online.

19:20.360 --> 19:22.440
Yifan, you've been following this story.

19:22.520 --> 19:24.600
So, you'll need to stay a few more days
to cover the follow-up reports.

19:24.680 --> 19:26.320
- Okay.
- Alright.

19:26.400 --> 19:29.080
If there's nothing else,
you all may head back and get some rest.

19:29.160 --> 19:30.160
Take a good rest.

19:30.240 --> 19:31.440
We'll head back now, Ms. Qian.

19:31.520 --> 19:32.640
Okay.

19:32.720 --> 19:34.280
It seems

19:34.360 --> 19:36.440
it will be difficult to return
before his birthday.

19:38.840 --> 19:41.680
I've already told my mom.

19:41.760 --> 19:43.240
I'm not going abroad with her.

19:43.920 --> 19:46.400
I'll stay here to be with Dad.

19:47.160 --> 19:49.720
I gave up custody before because…

19:50.440 --> 19:53.640
my ex-wife could provide
a better life for Yu.

19:53.720 --> 19:55.320
Our marriage didn't last…

19:55.400 --> 19:57.800
- I want to be with Dad now…
- It's not just about her.

19:57.880 --> 20:00.200
- I'm not leaving…
- Should we

20:00.280 --> 20:02.160
have Yu avoid this topic?

20:02.240 --> 20:03.360
No need.

20:04.000 --> 20:05.800
She's already grown up.

20:06.800 --> 20:08.360
We used to be a family.

20:09.480 --> 20:11.200
She has the right to know all of this.

20:12.960 --> 20:14.600
And through this experience,

20:14.680 --> 20:16.520
I see

20:17.040 --> 20:19.680
Yu has become stronger and braver.

20:20.360 --> 20:21.520
Right, Yu?

20:25.480 --> 20:27.320
- Can you hold on for a bit?
- Okay.

20:35.840 --> 20:36.720
Okay.

20:41.360 --> 20:42.400
Ms. Li!

20:42.480 --> 20:43.520
Ms. Li!

20:46.760 --> 20:49.120
Don't you really consider
giving us an interview?

20:50.760 --> 20:51.800
No.

20:52.720 --> 20:55.560
I understand you must have your reasons.

21:08.080 --> 21:10.680
You probably don't want
to give up custody either.

21:15.840 --> 21:17.640
Back when I was with Shi Lei,

21:18.520 --> 21:20.360
we fought a lot about money.

21:23.080 --> 21:24.600
Looking back now,

21:24.680 --> 21:26.440
I realize life is really fragile.

21:27.400 --> 21:29.360
Staying with the person you love safely

21:30.040 --> 21:31.400
and leaving no regrets

21:32.360 --> 21:34.200
are already the greatest happiness.

21:38.160 --> 21:40.440
Honestly, I don't care what others say.

21:41.600 --> 21:42.800
I just don't want to hurt Yu.

21:44.080 --> 21:46.200
Mom, why are you over there?

21:46.280 --> 21:47.920
Why aren't you coming over?

21:50.840 --> 21:52.240
Come on. Give me a hug.

22:01.160 --> 22:02.640
Leaving no regrets…

22:03.400 --> 22:04.440
Don't cry.

22:12.640 --> 22:16.160
I hope every story in this world
can have a happy ending.

22:16.240 --> 22:17.520
That's a great thing to say.

22:18.800 --> 22:20.560
Yifan, are we heading back
to the hotel now?

22:20.640 --> 22:21.760
Wen Yifan.

22:24.480 --> 22:26.480
What's wrong? Did you meet someone?

22:27.080 --> 22:29.720
- Did you run into someone you know?
- No.

22:31.280 --> 22:33.200
Did you guys hear someone calling my name?

22:33.280 --> 22:36.680
I'm not sure. But I think so.
I think it was a man.

22:37.560 --> 22:38.400
I didn't hear it.

22:57.840 --> 22:59.120
Happy birthday.

23:01.000 --> 23:02.880
Luckily, it's just past midnight.

23:06.600 --> 23:07.600
- Hello.
- Hello.

23:08.160 --> 23:12.120
I ordered a cake for you. It should arrive
at your place around noon.

23:12.200 --> 23:13.480
And as for the gift,

23:13.560 --> 23:15.320
I'll get it for you
when I come back, okay?

23:17.360 --> 23:18.840
You seem pretty sincere.

23:19.560 --> 23:21.280
It's worth my 70 days of reporting.

23:21.360 --> 23:23.680
But I can't return today.

23:23.760 --> 23:25.520
I won't be back until tomorrow.

23:30.920 --> 23:34.080
And… happy birthday.

23:51.920 --> 23:55.360
Let's consider my birthday this year
to be tomorrow.

23:57.000 --> 23:59.160
There is one more day left.

23:59.240 --> 24:00.760
…one more day left.

24:08.440 --> 24:11.800
JANUARY 2

24:36.200 --> 24:37.360
It's still raining.

24:38.960 --> 24:40.160
Did I wake you up?

24:40.800 --> 24:41.920
Yifan,

24:42.440 --> 24:44.040
aren't you sleepy at all?

24:55.680 --> 25:00.560
BEIYU HIGH SCHOOL

25:10.560 --> 25:11.840
How did the exam go this morning?

25:12.600 --> 25:14.200
It went well this morning.

25:14.280 --> 25:17.120
I'll keep pushing this afternoon.
And I'll do even better tomorrow.

25:55.680 --> 25:59.920
BEIYU NOSTALGIC NOODLES

26:19.280 --> 26:22.560
MEET THE ONE YOU LOVE AGAIN AND AGAIN

26:44.320 --> 26:45.760
Your dishes are here.

27:17.920 --> 27:19.920
DEDICATED TO NOODLES

27:22.920 --> 27:26.280
BEIYU NOSTALGIC NOODLES

27:27.800 --> 27:30.320
Everything's still the same as before.

27:35.080 --> 27:36.520
What would you like to eat?

27:40.080 --> 27:41.320
I'll…

27:42.920 --> 27:44.200
I'll take a bowl of wonton noodles.

27:50.880 --> 27:53.960
Girl, it's you!

27:54.040 --> 27:55.720
Long time no see!

27:55.800 --> 27:56.840
Yeah.

27:58.320 --> 28:01.400
After the college entrance exam,
I haven't lived in this city.

28:01.480 --> 28:03.960
Alright, hold on for a bit.
I'm going to cook your noodles.

28:04.040 --> 28:05.960
- No rush. Take your time.
- Alright.

28:25.000 --> 28:28.480
BEIYU NOSTALGIC NOODLES

28:32.800 --> 28:36.480
BEIYU, ALWAYS RAINING

28:40.240 --> 28:44.000
You haven't posted on Moments in ages.
What's going on today?

28:54.920 --> 28:58.880
WHEN YOU'RE OLD, I WON'T FORGET
THE TIME WE SPENT TOGETHER

29:22.120 --> 29:23.600
Your dish is here.

29:23.680 --> 29:25.320
It's rare for you
to come back and support.

29:25.400 --> 29:26.680
Try it.

29:26.760 --> 29:28.560
See if it tastes the same
as when you were a kid.

29:29.080 --> 29:30.120
Thanks.

29:32.080 --> 29:33.160
It's raining again.

29:33.680 --> 29:35.160
It's getting cold.

29:35.240 --> 29:36.120
Enjoy your meal.

29:43.560 --> 29:45.560
That day, when we broke up in the rain…

29:47.080 --> 29:49.880
I saw an expression on his face
I'd never seen.

29:53.960 --> 29:55.600
Sang Yan deserves…

30:02.320 --> 30:04.960
all the good things in the world.

30:09.880 --> 30:11.320
Back then,

30:12.400 --> 30:14.200
he was such a brilliant youth.

30:18.360 --> 30:20.200
I'll definitely get into Nanwu University.

30:20.280 --> 30:22.280
You deserve all the good things.

30:36.280 --> 30:38.640
I should be brave for him this time.

30:43.200 --> 30:44.640
This time, I'll take the initiative.

30:54.960 --> 30:56.000
Sang Yan.

30:56.560 --> 30:57.680
What's wrong?

30:58.880 --> 31:01.240
Does what you said before still count?

31:01.960 --> 31:03.120
What did I say?

31:04.600 --> 31:05.720
You said…

31:09.160 --> 31:11.120
You said if I pursued you,
you might consider it.

31:11.200 --> 31:14.000
I'm just letting you know about this
in advance. Think about it.

31:22.640 --> 31:23.880
I am…

31:25.120 --> 31:26.640
not that bad, right?

31:29.280 --> 31:30.440
Of course not.

32:20.800 --> 32:21.920
Girl,

32:22.000 --> 32:24.280
I think this rain
isn't going to stop anytime soon.

32:24.360 --> 32:25.320
Let me give you an umbrella.

32:26.040 --> 32:27.880
I want to stay here a bit longer.

32:27.960 --> 32:28.960
Let's wait for the rain to stop, okay?

32:29.040 --> 32:30.280
Alright, no problem.

32:33.480 --> 32:34.720
I probably…

32:35.240 --> 32:37.320
won't come here again.

32:38.680 --> 32:40.120
I just want to stay here a bit longer.

32:41.560 --> 32:43.040
It all feels

32:43.560 --> 32:45.600
like a dream.

32:50.160 --> 32:52.000
Handsome, what would you like?

32:53.080 --> 32:54.240
Maybe next time.

32:58.960 --> 33:01.640
This time… I'm here to pick someone up.

33:51.000 --> 33:51.840
It's you!

33:52.440 --> 33:54.440
Earlier, I saw this girl coming alone.

33:54.520 --> 33:56.920
I thought you two
weren't in contact anymore.

33:57.000 --> 33:59.920
That's great. After all these years,
you're still together.

34:01.120 --> 34:02.920
Next time we come to Beiyu,
I'll take care of your business again.

34:03.000 --> 34:04.040
Alright.

34:06.200 --> 34:07.040
How come you're here?

34:08.159 --> 34:09.000
Through the magic door.

34:13.600 --> 34:15.159
You finished all the food? Want some more?

34:18.080 --> 34:18.960
How did you know I was here?

34:20.920 --> 34:22.480
Whenever I come to Beiyu, I stop by here.

34:34.639 --> 34:35.800
What are you looking at?

34:37.920 --> 34:39.880
I was thinking, if I were a boss,

34:41.320 --> 34:42.960
what kind of store would I open here?

34:44.320 --> 34:45.679
Did you think of something?

34:52.520 --> 34:53.719
What about you?

34:53.800 --> 34:55.960
If it were you,
what kind of store would you open?

34:56.960 --> 34:58.000
Me?

35:00.200 --> 35:01.480
I…

35:02.720 --> 35:03.640
I want to open a small shop.

35:05.160 --> 35:06.320
This place's not large, already.

35:06.400 --> 35:08.000
I'm talking about the kind

35:08.080 --> 35:11.320
where you can stay as long as you want
and where you can relieve your stress.

35:17.200 --> 35:19.640
I want it to be a place

35:20.760 --> 35:23.280
where students can come to have noodles

35:23.360 --> 35:24.200
and read books after school.

35:25.400 --> 35:28.520
Where people can come in
for some food after work.

35:28.600 --> 35:30.800
I'd also play my favorite music for them.

36:11.800 --> 36:13.000
At that time,

36:13.080 --> 36:16.320
customers here
can work while eating noodles,

36:16.400 --> 36:17.520
without the feeling of overtime.

36:21.040 --> 36:22.080
What?

36:26.720 --> 36:28.320
Is that still a noodle shop?

36:29.560 --> 36:31.920
It doesn't matter.
This is the kind of shop I like.

36:35.440 --> 36:36.640
Good.

36:37.640 --> 36:39.200
Good for what?

36:39.280 --> 36:42.400
When I have money,
I'll buy this place and open you

36:42.480 --> 36:43.960
a small shop
for relaxation and stress relief.

36:47.040 --> 36:47.880
That's my wish.

36:47.960 --> 36:49.040
- What does that have to do with you?
- It's settled then.

36:49.800 --> 36:50.960
Eat up.

37:02.760 --> 37:05.960
When I have money,
I'll buy this place and open you

37:06.040 --> 37:07.440
a small shop
for relaxation and stress relief.

37:08.680 --> 37:12.280
Reporter Wen, you've been working overtime
for a whole week.

37:12.360 --> 37:14.920
My friend said a new restaurant
just opened on Gastropub Street,

37:15.000 --> 37:16.720
and the boss is really handsome.

37:24.880 --> 37:27.440
I'm the boss of Overtime.
My surname is Sang.

37:33.800 --> 37:39.200
BEIYU NOSTALGIC NOODLES

37:40.160 --> 37:41.200
Hold this.

38:06.280 --> 38:07.160
Give it to me.

38:14.760 --> 38:15.920
Wen Shuangjiang.

38:20.040 --> 38:21.160
There are some things

38:22.040 --> 38:24.200
I've always thought
too pretentious to say.

38:26.520 --> 38:28.280
Even saying a single word

38:28.960 --> 38:30.280
felt embarrassing.

38:38.720 --> 38:39.880
But in this life,

38:42.480 --> 38:43.400
I have to say it once.

38:46.960 --> 38:48.000
Haven't you…

38:49.480 --> 38:50.480
noticed yet?

38:53.760 --> 38:55.000
After all these years,

38:57.840 --> 38:58.960
I still…

39:01.400 --> 39:02.600
only like you.

39:40.360 --> 39:43.320
BEIYU NOSTALGIC NOODLES

39:43.400 --> 39:44.560
Say something.

39:51.200 --> 39:52.160
If…

39:52.240 --> 39:55.760
you think saying these words
are too pretentious…

39:56.960 --> 39:58.280
then let me say them from now on.

40:04.240 --> 40:06.200
Though, right now,

40:06.720 --> 40:08.800
it's a little hard for me to say them.

40:11.840 --> 40:13.400
We're…

40:14.440 --> 40:15.560
We're now…

40:17.600 --> 40:19.160
We're…

40:19.240 --> 40:22.480
We're mutually in love.

40:39.720 --> 40:41.760
So, from now on…

40:44.760 --> 40:46.520
you're my boyfriend?

40:52.600 --> 40:53.680
Yes!

41:02.360 --> 41:03.640
Are you really this happy?

41:05.240 --> 41:06.480
Well,

41:07.320 --> 41:10.160
to get a man as extraordinary as me,

41:11.000 --> 41:13.080
it's definitely worth
celebrating for ages.

41:15.880 --> 41:17.000
Let's go back.

41:21.000 --> 41:22.640
Move the umbrella over to your side a bit.

41:22.720 --> 41:23.880
You're all wet.

41:23.960 --> 41:25.400
Wen Shuangjiang,

41:26.200 --> 41:28.920
when enjoying someone else's service,
could you have fewer complaints?

41:29.880 --> 41:31.240
Also,

41:31.320 --> 41:33.320
you deserve to be treated this way.

41:40.800 --> 41:42.720
- What are you looking at?
- I want to buy something.

41:44.680 --> 41:45.840
I want two apples.

41:45.920 --> 41:47.760
- Got it.
- You want to eat apples?

41:48.760 --> 41:50.160
I promised to get you the real one.

42:14.000 --> 42:19.920
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

42:20.000 --> 42:22.000
Let's consider my birthday this year

42:22.080 --> 42:23.280
to be tomorrow.

42:27.120 --> 42:29.320
There's one more day left.

42:54.920 --> 43:01.760
NANWU TO BEIYU

43:09.360 --> 43:10.880
WEN YIFAN

43:16.280 --> 43:17.120
Sang Yan.

43:17.880 --> 43:18.960
What's wrong?

43:19.880 --> 43:22.160
Does what you said before still count?

43:23.160 --> 43:24.200
You said…

43:25.360 --> 43:27.800
You said if I pursued you,
you might consider it.

43:28.640 --> 43:31.840
I'm just letting you know about this
in advance. Think about it.

44:22.320 --> 44:24.160
Handsome, what would you like?

44:25.040 --> 44:26.160
Maybe next time.

44:26.240 --> 44:29.000
This time… I'm here to pick someone up.

47:16.400 --> 47:17.280
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

47:17.360 --> 47:18.280
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
